ven.&amp;nbsp; Use steam or water. Colonize the monotub at normal room temperature too.&amp;nbsp; Be sure to place a weight on the straw to hold it compressed during colonization.&lt;br /&gt;RR</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>16135502</next>\n<prev>16132119</prev>\n<first>16131182</first>\n<last>16135502</last>\n<when>1335272292</when>\n<utime>04/24/12 03:58 PM</utime>\n</post>"}